util.object

Class AbstractWrapper<T>

  • java.lang.Object
    • util.object.AbstractWrapper<T>
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.util.function.Supplier<T>
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    ResourceLocation, Wrapper

    public abstract class AbstractWrapper<T>
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.util.function.Supplier<T>
    A Supplier to wrap a value in such a way that the wrapper behaves just like the wrapped value in terms of equality, hashing, and string conversion.
